    "id": "v11"
  }, "v11"), mdx("p", null, "Khi Na-than nghe v\u1EADy li\u1EC1n \u0111i g\u1EB7p B\xE1t-s\xEA-ba, m\u1EB9 c\u1EE7a S\xF4-l\xF4-m\xF4n. Na-than h\u1ECFi, \"B\xE0 c\xF3 nghe tin A-\u0111\xF4-ni-gia, con trai Ha-gh\xEDt, t\u1EF1 phong m\xECnh l\xE0m vua ch\u01B0a? Ch\u1EE7 ch\xFAng ta l\xE0 \u0110a-v\xEDt kh\xF4ng hay bi\u1EBFt g\xEC v\u1EC1 chuy\u1EC7n \u1EA5y c\u1EA3. "), mdx("h6", {
