  }, "v13"), mdx("p", null, "H\xE3y \u0111i v\xE0o g\u1EB7p vua \u0110a-v\xEDt n\xF3i, 'Th\u01B0a vua ch\xFAa t\xF4i, b\u1EC7 h\u1EA1 \u0111\xE3 h\u1EE9a l\xE0 S\xF4-l\xF4-m\xF4n con trai t\xF4i s\u1EBD l\xE0m vua v\xE0 l\xEAn ng\xF4i k\u1EBF v\u1ECB b\u1EC7 h\u1EA1. V\u1EADy t\u1EA1i sao A-\u0111\xF4-ni-gia \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m vua r\u1ED3i?' "), mdx("h6", {
