  }, "v25"), mdx("p", null, "H\xF4m nay anh ta \u0111\xE3 gi\u1EBFt nhi\u1EC1u b\xF2, b\xEA m\u1EADp, chi\xEAn v\xE0 m\u1EDDi c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u1EDDi con kh\xE1c c\u1EE7a vua, c\xE1c c\u1EA5p ch\u1EC9 huy qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i c\xF9ng th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 A-bia-tha. Hi\u1EC7n gi\u1EDD h\u1ECD \u0111ang \u0103n u\u1ED1ng v\u1EDBi anh ta. H\u1ECD k\xEAu l\xEAn, 'Vua A-\u0111\xF4-ni-gia v\u1EA1n tu\u1EBF!' "), mdx("h6", {
