  }, "v34"), mdx("p", null, "Th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 Xa-\u0111\u1ED1c, ti\xEAn tri Na-than s\u1EBD \u0111\u1ED5 d\u1EA7u tr\xEAn n\xF3 t\u1EA1i \u0111\xF3 v\xE0 c\u1EED n\xF3 l\xE0m vua tr\xEAn \xCDt-ra-en. H\xE3y th\u1ED5i k\xE8n v\xE0 h\xF4 to, 'Vua S\xF4-l\xF4-m\xF4n v\u1EA1n tu\u1EBF!' "), mdx("h6", {
