    "id": "v36"
  }, "v36"), mdx("p", null, "B\xEA-na-gia, con Gi\xEA-h\xF4-gia-\u0111a th\u01B0a v\u1EDBi vua, \"A-men ! C\u1EA7u CH\xDAA, l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF c\u1EE7a ch\u1EE7 t\xF4i \u0111\u1ED3ng \xFD! "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v37"
  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA lu\xF4n lu\xF4n gi\xFAp \u0111\u1EE1 b\u1EC7 h\u1EA1, vua ch\xFAng t\xF4i. C\u1EA7u CH\xDAA c\u0169ng s\u1EBD gi\xFAp S\xF4-l\xF4-m\xF4n v\xE0 khi\u1EBFn cho ng\xF4i ng\u01B0\u1EDDi cao tr\u1ECDng h\u01A1n c\u1EA3 ng\xF4i b\u1EC7 h\u1EA1 n\u1EEFa.\" "), mdx("h6", {
